{"tid":1540832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那網民：港獨廢青贏了，中央輸了","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:56:28.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6aac65aa6f71d9a0abb66963838272647e9bf96a","tid":1540832,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"香港特首林鄭月娥今日宣佈「撤回」修訂逃犯條例，但卻拒絕成立獨立調查委員會，中國《新京報》率先在微博上報道，但是這新聞下的留言部份，有逾百人留言，卻沒顯示出來。對於林鄭最終撤回惡法，亦不少網民討論時都感到驚訝，有網民直言：「林鄭月娥撤回反送條例，香港港獨廢青贏了，中央輸了，港府輸了！」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都驚訝林鄭會作出這個決定，說：「這次妥協，下次就不是香港鬧了，就換內地了！」「沒輸？暴亂就答應訴求，你讓14億雙眼睛學到了甚麼？」「不想妄議政治，如果真是這樣，中美貿易戰你也認輸算了。」<br />\n<br />\n可是，有網民卻不認為這是「輸」了：「​​​​關中央屁事？」「贊同，這是給港獨一個套！」「大家別理他啊，甚麼輸贏？中央甚麼時候跟你們鬥過？你們自己搞的事情自己解決？」亦有網民稱，消息令港股下午急升，說：「肯定是我們要贏錢，股市代表國運能力，你覺得廢青贏了，股市不會崩才怪！」<br />\n<br />\n有網民認為事件背後肯定有問題：「感覺有蹊蹺，這個讓步肯定是得讓廢青付出代價，或者是更強行措施的開始！」「你看不看的懂形勢啊就在這帶節奏？明顯港府在下套好嗎！」"},{"pid":"6e4d1edb48383a8f6c076946aa3cc53acad769e9","tid":1540832,"uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190904/large/1567591942_4d27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190904%2Flarge%2F1567591942_4d27.jpg&h=6d531268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國傳媒報道林鄭撤回的消息，但不顯示網民留言。"},{"pid":"fbc1e0efeec40f20afe5672977a7250696659bb7","tid":1540832,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190904/60009394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190904%2F60009394&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbhjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=35f49fdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190904%2F60009394&h=63270cbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190904/60009394</a>"},{"pid":"4e30c136560287f483ca23038d8936c606081e8b","tid":1540832,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:40:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91c08dfaf5c00ace7895bd451e657e4eb1215b59","tid":1540832,"uid":186851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"連支那人都知係圈套，唔好慶祝住"},{"pid":"f8cf4c5d24344b2a846cd63fba336000eb8e2ddf","tid":1540832,"uid":260238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"柒婆想分散注意力！太子一定死咗人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540764</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【831 太子站目擊者立法會見記者】<br />\n-有一個人失蹤<br />\n-有機會有一個人死左 比警察打左半個鐘 嘔白泡 差佬見佢冇反應 之後冇打 二三十分鐘後由消防員 非救護人員 送走 完全冇反應<br />\n-差佬同佢地講強姦佢地係正常<br />\n-有被捕人士係警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n-係警署去廁所時不能關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在埋<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲要係人權法推之前動議徹回，呢隻老狐狸都老奸巨滑啦</span>"},{"pid":"7f91a7a55362a1fd1521ff2ae40e7ccf2bd27d6f","tid":1540832,"uid":78429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"「這次妥協，下次就不是香港鬧了，就換內地了！」<br />\n<br />\n十月一天安門示威!"},{"pid":"db7d8d381fb4e4bbb850c00132f5160cb3e8099b","tid":1540832,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:55:34.000Z","msg":"We have five demands. Withdrawal of the amendment bill is only one of them. The five demands are:<br />\n1. Full withdrawal of the extradition bill <br />\n2. A commission of inquiry into alleged police brutality <br />\n3. Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo; <br />\n4. Amnesty for arrested protesters <br />\n5. Dual universal suffrage for both the Legislative Council and<br />\nthe Chief Executive <br />\nThe 2nd, 3rd, and the 4th demands arise because the government refused to withdraw the bill amendment after a marching of 1 million Hong Kong people. The 5th demand is the ultimate solution of the turmoil in Hong Kong. <br />\nNow the government withdraws the bill, and it is not a concession at all. It&rsquo;s only a tactic of the government trying to kill the movement by the people. <br />\n<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS NOT ONE LESS"},{"pid":"9b10a7447deaec3f93cc898ed94ef039da995604","tid":1540832,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f91a7a55362a1fd1521ff2ae40e7ccf2bd27d6f","tid":1540832,"uid":78429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"「這次妥協，下次就不是香港鬧了，就換內地了！」<br />\n<br />\n十月一天安門示威!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"反貴價豬肉遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7ada9c260225aec98eea1d821fc2fcf87d5b91","tid":1540832,"uid":299779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"⚠️⚠️麻煩推爆佢，話比啲外國人知單嘢未完⚠️⚠️<br />\n<br />\n[英］Response to Lam&rsquo;s withdrawal of the bill <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1540599/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1540599/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d623d3d660c40206c7dd34e7c12607aca3976fd","tid":1540832,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b10a7447deaec3f93cc898ed94ef039da995604","tid":1540832,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f91a7a55362a1fd1521ff2ae40e7ccf2bd27d6f","tid":1540832,"uid":78429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"「這次妥協，下次就不是香港鬧了，就換內地了！」<br />\n<br />\n十月一天安門示威!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"反貴價豬肉遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"各省谷縣增設costco<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58be415483c7428ce82baea8a31ed05e1db2c22","tid":1540832,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6735b837f4e1a27e4cf55c9b1c8ba267422d6dd3","tid":1540832,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"尋釁滋事<br />\n中國從來唔會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}